flowchart TD
    A[Application Source Code] --> B[Bundler Analyzes Dependency Graph]
    B --> C{Split strategy?}
    C --> D[Entry-Point Split]
    C --> E[Dynamic Import Split]
    C --> F[Vendor Split]
    D --> G[Chunk per App Entry Point]
    E --> H[Chunk per dynamic import boundary]
    F --> I[Shared vendor libraries chunk]
    G --> J[Chunk Manifest Generated]
    H --> J
    I --> J
    J --> K[Output: main.hash.js + async chunks]
    K --> L[Initial Page Load — Download main.js Only]
    L --> M[App Boots and Renders Initial Route]
    M --> N{User navigates to new route?}
    N -- Route chunk not loaded --> O[Runtime Inserts script tag for chunk]
    O --> P[Browser Downloads Route Chunk]
    P --> Q[Execute Chunk and Render Route]
    N -- Chunk cached --> Q
    style L fill:#3b82f6,color:#fff
    style Q fill:#22c55e,color:#fff
